# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Mapbox token — powers ALL map features:
#   • Globe projection + satellite/streets/terrain/navigation styles
#   • Real-world geocoding search (countries, cities, streets, POIs)
#   • Mapbox Directions API (driving/walking/cycling routes)
#   • Live POI fetch (restaurants, hotels, landmarks near any location)
#   • 3D buildings, terrain elevation, sky layer
# Get yours free at: https://account.mapbox.com/
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1IjoiWU9VUl9VU0VSTkFNRSIsImEiOiJZT1VSX0tFWSJ9.XXXXX

# ── Optional ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenAI — for live AI travel insights (the app has offline AI by default)
VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here

# Weather API key (OpenWeatherMap)
VITE_WEATHER_API_KEY=your_weather_api_key_here

# Backend URL (optional — for server-side features)
